in root folder of project (to make sure it exists)
tsc --version

then, to create tsconfig.json
tsc --init

then, to set up a watch
tsc -w

Edit the tscconfig.json
set target to es2021 <-- or whatever is latest
set module to es2020
sourcemap to true
outdir to ./dist
rootdir to ./src

create html, css and js directories in dist
create ts files in src

start LiveServer from html

Let the fun begin!